# .mailmap — canonicalize commit identities in git log and GitHub UI
#
# Syntax:
#   Canonical Name <canonical@email>   Commit Name <commit@email>
#
# All past commits made under alternate identities (VS Code / MCP / tooling
# sessions) are unified here under the canonical maintainer identity.
# History SHAs are preserved; only the displayed author name/email changes.

